drop table "CON_DiscounttStatusCode" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "CON_DiscounttStatusCode" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "CON_DiscounttStatusCode"
(
"DiscountStatusID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"StatusCode" VARCHAR(20) not null,
"Enable" INTEGER default 1 not null,
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP not null,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32) not null,
constraint PK_CON_DISCOUNTTSTATUSCODE primary key ("DiscountStatusID")
);

comment on column "CON_DiscounttStatusCode"."StatusCode" is
'10：创建未提交
20：提交待批准
30：审批通过
40：通过未使用
41：提交待财务确定
50：已变更使用到合同
51：财务不同意使用优惠
';

comment on column "CON_DiscounttStatusCode"."Enable" is
'1:有效 0:无效';
